This repository contains two categories of software with different licensing:

OPEN SOURCE (Apache 2.0):
  - Spoke runtime (src/framework/, src/agent/, src/types/)
  - Agent SDK and contract specification (specs/foundational/)
  - Test infrastructure (test/)
  - Helm chart (deploy/)

COMMERCIAL (All Rights Reserved):
  - Hub API server, coordination engine, and management UI
    (not included in this repository — available via crisismode.ai)
  - Hub analytics, multi-tenant coordination, and enrichment services

The spoke runtime and agent SDK are designed to operate independently
for development, testing, and single-spoke deployments. The commercial
hub provides centralized coordination, analytics, and management for
multi-spoke enterprise deployments.

